        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3299335501" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer87447701144205934">A bit of childhood nostalgia, I probably read this 50 times in middle school. Let me tell you, it really holds up! What an incredible writer and a beautiful, intricate story. I finished it last night and spent all morning listening to the music the protagonist plays throughout the story. I also spent some time researching Mozart. Fun fact: dude was really into scatological humor. Anyway, read this masterpiece and rock out to Mozart.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


