              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer266652301774428397">Absolutely amazing. <br/>This book is about a young violinist who has to learn how to truly connect to the music and Mozart, and all the struggles inbetween. The relations and character in this story are outstanding, though this book does have a slower pace. I would recommend this book to any musician, particularly classical, from the ages 12 and up.</span>

          </span>
